- Mom, please!

356
00:25:31,240 --> 00:25:33,400
- Come here.
- Mom!

357
00:25:37,000 --> 00:25:38,360
Radwa.

358
00:25:40,080 --> 00:25:41,840
Radwa, my child!

359
