369
00:26:26,800 --> 00:26:30,719
You don't respect me as a husband at all.

370
00:26:30,720 --> 00:26:32,760
You don't respect me at all!

371
00:26:34,400 --> 00:26:37,479
Okay, you've been asking
all this while, right?

372
00:26:37,480 --> 00:26:39,719
You've been asking all this while, right?

373
