T.

378
00:26:58,640 --> 00:26:59,520
H.

379
00:27:04,320 --> 00:27:05,200
A.

380
00:27:06,320 --> 00:27:08,000
R.

381
00:27:09,520 --> 00:27:10,600
I.

382
