- Hey, darling.

383
00:27:15,840 --> 00:27:18,559
Look at me. Please listen to me.

384
00:27:18,560 --> 00:27:20,399
Inhale.

385
00:27:20,400 --> 00:27:21,600
Exhale.

386
00:27:23,080 --> 00:27:24,160
One.

387
00:27:24,760 --> 00:27:26,359
Two.

388
00:27:26,360 --> 00:27:27,640
Three.

389
00:27:29,640 --> 00:27:31,399
We'll go home.

390
00:27:31,400 --> 00:27:32,880
Okay?

391
